
Todo:

Nuget packages:
  - Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Sqlite --> used in Startup.cs to manage the DBContext
  - AlertifyJs: 
    - Handles alerts in a SPA
    - npm install alertifyjs --save
  - JwtHelperService:
    - Handling of JWT Tokens
    - npm install @auth0/angular-jwt
  - Ngx Bootstrap:
    - Angular Component Templates
    - npm install ngx-bootstrap --save
  - Bootswatch:
    - Design templates with many stype themes
    - npm install bootswatch

Best Practices:
  - Use asyncronous methods to retrieve data from the database
  - The Token in appsettings.json should be a randomly generated string of big length
  - Routing Guards:
    - Generated via Angular CLI: ng g guard <name>

API:
  - Cors is needed when using different services (like API and Angular application) 